#phrase Hero2 1
Hello Blacksmith! Is the fire burning hot in your furnaces? It is a pleasure to meet a man of your profession, especially when you need his services.
#ANIMATION 17
#CAMERA 5
#phrase Zaku 2
Yes, may the Great Powers help you too, stranger of men. And though I am a blacksmith and take pride in my craft, I will not create anything for you.
#ANIMATION 11
#CAMERA 5
#phrase Hero2 3
But why this? Are you afraid I'll pay you with counterfeit coins?
#ANIMATION 6
#CAMERA 5
#phrase Zaku 4
That's not the point. As long as you're a stranger here, it's like you don't exist for us. And when you become one of us, then everyone will be happy to help you. Including me.